      "Title": "GardaVettingSystem.Pages.ApplicantAddresses.DeleteModel",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/GardaVettingSystem.Pages.ApplicantAddresses.DeleteModel.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Handles the deletion of an address belonging to the logged-in applicant.</p>\n<p>Ownership is verified server-side — users can only delete their own addresses.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "ManagedReference",
      "source_relative_path": "api/GardaVettingSystem.Pages.ApplicantAddresses.EditModel.yml",
