      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/GardaVettingSystem.Pages.ApplicantAddresses.EditModel.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Handles the editing of an existing address belonging to the logged-in applicant.</p>\n<p>Ownership is verified server-side on both GET and POST — users can only edit their own addresses.</p>\n<p>ApplicantNumber is always set server-side and never accepted from the form.</p>\n"
    },
